{"tid":2249492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉協助運送羅漢齋飯進收押所　3人獲撤銷控罪准自簽守行為15個月","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T16:14:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2798d39e2afeab670c867ccfbc5bcc8e48bfcc36","tid":2249492,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"2016年旺角大衝突中被控暴動罪，審訊後被裁定罪名不成立的林傲軒，涉聯同荔枝角收押所其中一間膳食供應商的兩名員工，偷運一盒羅漢齋飯予一名收押者，遭懲教人員發現。3人被指違反《監獄條例》，被控將未獲授權物品引進監獄等罪，今（19日）在西九龍裁判法院獲准以現金1000元自簽守行為15個月，控罪獲撤。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，林傲軒於2月15日到荔枝角收押所探望一名牽涉2016旺角及2019理大暴動還押男子連潤發，當時對話內容有錄音，懲教人員亦在監察，人員聽到林傲軒跟連潤發說「同你入咗飯，晏晝應該有齋食」，遂報告上級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201019/s00001/1603101695819/%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E5%81%B7%E9%81%8B%E7%BE%85%E6%BC%A2%E9%BD%8B%E9%A3%AF%E9%80%B2%E6%94%B6%E6%8A%BC%E6%89%80-3%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%A4%E7%BD%AA%E5%87%86%E8%87%AA%E7%B0%BD%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201019%2Fs00001%2F1603101695819%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%2581%25B7%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%25BD%258B%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%258A%25BC%25E6%2589%2580-3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2587%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=7c9dc575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201019%2Fs00001%2F1603101695819%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%2581%25B7%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%25BD%258B%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%258A%25BC%25E6%2589%2580-3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2587%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258